, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice A new supplement, the Maurten Bicarb System, is being used to fuel runners at theOlympicsbut a lack of comprehensive data has led to scepticism of its benefits.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"A new supplement\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"the Maurten Bicarb System\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"runners\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsbut\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"comprehensive data\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"scepticism\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"its benefits\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bicarb System is designed to elevate sodium bicarbonate in the blood by up to more than a third of its normal levels.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Bicarb System\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"sodium bicarbonate\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"the blood\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"up to more than a third\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"its normal levels\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Contained within the \\u00a315 product is a mixing bowl, a hydrogel component and a bicarbonate component, used to produce a carbohydrate-rich sports drink.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gel\", \"score\": 0.902804932918348, \"rank\": 0.10765898981904543, \"text\": \"hydrogel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\u00a315 product\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"a mixing bowl\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"a bicarbonate component\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"a carbohydrate-rich sports drink\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Telegraphhas reported that more than 80 per cent of elite runners are estimated to be using this product which, given that it was only first introduced earlier last year, remains in its infancy.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Telegraphhas\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 80 per cent\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"elite runners\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"this product\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"its infancy\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Swedish endurance nutrition brand was created in 2015, Maurten swiftly became known for providing gels, solid bars, and drink mixes.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9991765152248256, \"rank\": 0.0008211710354158782, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maurten\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"gels\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"solid bars\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"mixes\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bicarb System, however, became its first product that was really catapulted into the limelight, with Maurten wishing to revolutionise the world ofathleticsahead ofParis 2024.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Bicarb System\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"its first product\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"the limelight\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"Maurten\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a sense, they were reintroducing what has historically been a commonly used substance, as athletes have previously been known for consuming raw sodium bicarbonate.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"a commonly used substance\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"raw sodium bicarbonate\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But while its performance-enhancing properties for endurance athletes are undisputable, the substance nonetheless lends itself to some cynicism.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its performance-enhancing properties\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance athletes\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"the substance\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"some cynicism\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peer-reviewed studies have not yet provided all of the necessary research to prove that the Bicarb System is safe to use beyond all reasonable doubt.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peer-reviewed studies\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"the necessary research\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bicarb System\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"all reasonable doubt\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sodium bicarbonate is a chemical compound which, when consumed directly, can increase the risk of cramping - a nightmare for any long-distance runner.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodium_bicarbonate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodium bicarbonate\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodium_bicarbonate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodium_bicarbonate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chemical compound\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"cramping\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"any long-distance runner\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, as athletes and coaches continue to experiment with the Bicarb System, its uncertainties, relating to a potentially heightened risk of injury, remain at the forefront of their minds.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bicarb System\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"its uncertainties\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"a potentially heightened risk\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the forefront\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"their minds\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That being said, the substance does seek to provide a proactive defence against hydrogen ions, which can cause discomfort in one's muscles during strenuous exercise.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the substance\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"a proactive defence\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"hydrogen ions\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"discomfort\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"one's muscles\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"strenuous exercise\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bicarb System was initially launched in February 2023, used by well-known cyclists Wout van Aert and Primoz Roglic.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wout van Aert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wout_van_Aert\"}, {\"begin\": 2514, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Primo\\u017e_Rogli\\u010d\", \"score\": 0.9999999999740794, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Primoz Roglic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Primo\\u017e_Rogli\\u010d\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Primo\\u017e_Rogli\\u010d\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Bicarb System\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"well-known cyclists\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, as Maurten's product was rapidly being endorsed in the world of cycling - leading to a noticeable surge in sales - Olympic gold medallist Jakob Ingebrigtsen became the first runner to promote the substance after winning gold in his 1500m race at the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2674, \"end\": 2692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maurten's product\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"a noticeable surge\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"the first runner\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the substance\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"his 1500m race\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soon, the Bicarb System became increasingly more popular among endurance athletes weighing between 60 and 70kg, and many of whom will no doubt be using it at Paris 2024, looking to gain a competitive edge.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 3013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Bicarb System\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance athletes\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"between 60 and 70kg\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2971}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitive edge\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3066, \"end\": 3077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.5704202656193e-12, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3228}]}]}"